ire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e42fdaea79a40091af20e86d2413f1bc8577b7","tid":1436764,"uid":4050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解一定係佢地開主題我地曬時間去駁佢？ 點解唔係我地開主題佢地之後回應我地</strong>？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想知<span style=\"color: green;\">鐳射筆，外國勢力，大台，經濟差</span><br />\n<br />\n想知<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>葉虎，同志們，過期彈呀</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e9fced3da491c58d5bfb092ff06d9df65dfa062e","tid":1436764,"uid":44751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d0b5905a084084ebfd406894dedb1969eaf95743","tid":1436764,"uid":107686,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:11:21.000Z","msg":"倒乜撚野戈 <br />\n人地依家係打經濟民生牌<br />\n警犬牌都已經証明左係廢既<br />\n起到拖政府後腿 仲唔割咩<br />\n<br />\n佢地已經用警犬撐過左8.5最勇武既時候<br />\ncondoms 用完就棄架la"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"依家唔係幫東方，係狙擊緊五毛留言<br />\n<br />\n假設你平時睇開東方，覺得今日篇報導奇奇怪怪，一睇留言，五毛齊屌，咁冇獨立思考能力嘅你，自然加入一齊屌<br />\n<br />\n調返轉頭，你見到下面啲留言讚報導中立持平，咁你自然睇多兩眼，一齊屌警察<br />\n<br />\n救得一個廢老多一個啊手足！"},{"pid":"0d7eb39b80f794abcc65819d0527f340188cafdc","tid":1436764,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"救廢老！救廢老！"},{"pid":"e1689b89649a702a59d2cf0e6bf2b5ba89792d1a","tid":1436764,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LzZJta3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLzZJta3.jpg&h=e30adf3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb699e1bce21e6c9a1931755bb6632adde270548","tid":1436764,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5471cbab88baedd983007194717ee767e6a203e","tid":1436764,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:20:22.000Z","msg":"東方真係好多呀叔睇嫁"},{"pid":"d3b28ed69ffe7754540f10c6cc18177c73731a4d","tid":1436764,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:21:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b9459efb6047faa3210ff0d1112a0d43ece52e59","tid":1436764,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"需要暫時支援東方"},{"pid":"5077f2f379b7699610b8284acb198bcec047a50a","tid":1436764,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢地私怨就算啦 仆住去幫手做咩"},{"pid":"1104ce0608bfa3597874ce6527910917b48cc3e7","tid":1436764,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960d9f688f8ce480caa4627736f9435366c57dc8","tid":1436764,"uid":78570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:24:14.000Z","msg":"每個禮拜五, 禮拜日都係全民儲錢日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n儲錢去旅行, 投資歐美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔好係香港燒肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劏房波話香港經濟轉差<br />\n咁香港人要儲錢來應對<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港好多黑社會可能會打劫銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係警察又怕左黑社會掉頭走喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以最好開埋外國離岸銀行戶口, 放D錢入去儲, 咁就安心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個禮拜五, 禮拜日都係全民儲錢日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n養成理財好習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家幫手係Facebook, twitter, tg wts group 做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436759/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436759/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手正皮. 推到熱門"},{"pid":"17a9ad45f664dde10628d5dd06a14ed0bfe9d7ae","tid":1436764,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:24:37.000Z","msg":"下，佢地講到亂到要解放軍入城wo"},{"pid":"045e7b030691fa37cc666f8ac9f39464e5b65f92","tid":1436764,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3e42fdaea79a40091af20e86d2413f1bc8577b7","tid":1436764,"uid":4050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解一定係佢地開主題我地曬時間去駁佢？ 點解唔係我地開主題佢地之後回應我地</strong>？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想知<span style=\"color: green;\">鐳射筆，外國勢力，大台，經濟差</span><br />\n<br />\n想知<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>葉虎，同志們，過期彈呀</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"係呀，所以快啲去東方FB度，提供呢啲資訊俾啲廢老大叔睇<br />\n<br />\n唔係講緊駁倒佢地，而係文宣工作黎，平時我地都留係同溫層，今次有東方助攻，可以食住個勢走出去，話俾啲大叔聽我地關注緊啲乜"},{"pid":"a42fbcbb1dd7815af283df0b9451e555196f5051","tid":1436764,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5077f2f379b7699610b8284acb198bcec047a50a","tid":1436764,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢地私怨就算啦 仆住去幫手做咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:30:08.000Z","msg":"冇人care東方，係東方班讀者啊"},{"pid":"acc3ccea615a52ea9e4b0cc8b5498739274a4d84","tid":1436764,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a42fbcbb1dd7815af283df0b9451e555196f5051","tid":1436764,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5077f2f379b7699610b8284acb198bcec047a50a","tid":1436764,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:22:43.000Z","msg"